sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant SearchBar as SearchBar.vue
    participant useSearch as useSearch composable
    participant Service as folderService
    participant API as Elysia API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (pg_trgm)

    User->>SearchBar: ketik karakter
    SearchBar->>useSearch: query.value = "..."
    useSearch->>useSearch: clearTimeout(timer)
    Note over useSearch: reset timer setiap keystroke

    User->>SearchBar: berhenti mengetik (300ms berlalu)
    useSearch->>useSearch: setTimeout fires
    useSearch->>Service: search(query, "all")
    Service->>API: GET /api/v1/search?q=...&type=all

    API->>DB: Promise.all([
    Note over API,DB: folderRepo.searchByName(q) — ILIKE %q% (GIN index)
    Note over API,DB: fileRepo.searchByName(q)   — ILIKE %q% (GIN index)
    DB-->>API: folders[] + files[] (max 50 each)

    API-->>Service: { folders, files, meta }
    Service-->>useSearch: SearchResultData
    useSearch-->>SearchBar: results.value = data
    SearchBar-->>User: tampilkan hasil di content panel
